name: Fairy Tail: Phoenix Priestess
description: The film revolves around a mysterious girl named Éclair who appears before Fairy Tail, the world's most notorious wizard's guild. The stones may spell the collapse of the magical world, and Natsu, Lucy, and the rest of the Fairy Tail guild are caught up in the intrigue.Fairy Tail: Phoenix Priestess featuring Aya Endo and Rie Kugimiya is streaming with subscription on Hulu, free on Tubi, available for rent or purchase on Microsoft Store, and 1 other.
